  m_text: "The Blue and Yelllow Cell cant be on the same side of the door.\n\nThe
    Red Cell is to the right of the Yellow cell.\n\nThe Yellow Cell has to be to
    the right of the door. \n\nThe Blue Cell is not closer to a window than the green
    cell."
